 <h3>Exponentiation and the remainder operators must be without a unit. Therefore we need to define an unitless scalar</h3>
 <p>
  <span class="eq">
   <var>scalar</var>
   <sub>unitless</sub>
   = 1.16
  </span>
 </p>
